survey_response.review_text: I had a planned pregnancy. After conceiving naturally I was consulting a leading doctor at a private hospital. However the experience wasn't great and not to our satisfaction. A friend of mine suggested Dr sathya and we made the right decision of starting to consult him from the 3rd month onwards. His calm demeanor, spending the right amount of time with patients explaining what the next steps are and what to expect , being reachable (most importantly), helped me to have a successful and smooth delivery. I would recommend him very strongly over all other gynaecologists in the city. Simply brilliant. Meet him once and you will know that you have made the right choice.

We were referred by another doctor. But he took time and understand the complete health situation from scracth.He always looks for the best possible treatment and explain in detail about the pros & cons of each treatment along with success rate. Instead of jumping into conclusion,he asked for a re-analysis.It came out that the previous test was wrong. He gave all the possible option and guided us to select the suitable one. Very calm and approachable person.

Dr.Sathya is very humble and patient in hearing our symptoms. I am consulting him for my pregnancy and I feel very comfortable in his approach. He explains the logic behind each tests and doesn't insist on taking medicines unless it is really required. He is warm and welcoming & I would definitely recommend him for anyone who asks me for an opinion
